    {"id":"f1nb","type":"rectangle","x":670,"y":100,"width":695,"height":295,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1d4ed8","backgroundColor":"#eff6ff","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":2100,"version":1,"versionNonce":2100,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746748800000,"index":"a18","link":null,"locked":false},
    {"id":"f1nt","type":"text","x":682,"y":108,"width":671,"height":280,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e2e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":2101,"version":1,"versionNonce":2101,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746748800000,"index":"a19","link":null,"locked":false,"text":"KEY INSIGHT: Per-Directory CLAUDE.md (not per-person)\n\nClaude Code auto-loads ALL CLAUDE.md files from current\ndirectory upward to root. Works automatically, no instruction.\n\n/CLAUDE.md         → always loaded (all roles, all sessions)\n/be/CLAUDE.md      → auto when working in /be/ (BE only)\n/fe/CLAUDE.md      → auto when working in /fe/ (FE only)\n/infra/CLAUDE.md   → auto when working in /infra/\n\nResult: BE sessions never see FE noise. FE sessions never\nsee BE linter rules. Less context = better focus = better output.\n\nDo NOT create one CLAUDE.md per person.\nDo create one per role subdirectory.\n\nFocus principle: CLAUDE.md root stays < 150 lines.\nIt is a MAP (pointers), not a TERRITORY (content).","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"KEY INSIGHT: Per-Directory CLAUDE.md (not per-person)\n\nClaude Code auto-loads ALL CLAUDE.md files from current\ndirectory upward to root. Works automatically, no instruction.\n\n/CLAUDE.md         → always loaded (all roles, all sessions)\n/be/CLAUDE.md      → auto when working in /be/ (BE only)\n/fe/CLAUDE.md      → auto when working in /fe/ (FE only)\n/infra/CLAUDE.md   → auto when working in /infra/\n\nResult: BE sessions never see FE noise. FE sessions never\nsee BE linter rules. Less context = better focus = better output.\n\nDo NOT create one CLAUDE.md per person.\nDo create one per role subdirectory.\n\nFocus principle: CLAUDE.md root stays < 150 lines.\nIt is a MAP (pointers), not a TERRITORY (content).","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":true},

