    {"id":"f2gt","type":"text","x":1420,"y":307,"width":1338,"height":86,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#92400e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":3081,"version":1,"versionNonce":3081,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746748800000,"index":"a34","link":null,"locked":false,"text":"TRACEABILITY RULE: Every task traces backward through all 4 levels. Example:\nTask 4-5 BE  →  Spec_4 §5.2 (PATCH /orders/:id/items)  →  SRS §4.3 (Chef updates status → trigger recalculate)  →  BRD §1.2 (KDS: update status per item)\nBreak anywhere in chain = wrong thing built. Task with no spec_ref = 🔴 STOP. Spec section not in BRD = 🔴 STOP. These are not optional checks.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"TRACEABILITY RULE: Every task traces backward through all 4 levels. Example:\nTask 4-5 BE  →  Spec_4 §5.2 (PATCH /orders/:id/items)  →  SRS §4.3 (Chef updates status → trigger recalculate)  →  BRD §1.2 (KDS: update status per item)\nBreak anywhere in chain = wrong thing built. Task with no spec_ref = 🔴 STOP. Spec section not in BRD = 🔴 STOP. These are not optional checks.","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":true},

