    {"id":"f3lt","type":"text","x":40,"y":465,"width":630,"height":244,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e2e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":4011,"version":1,"versionNonce":4011,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746748800000,"index":"a38","link":null,"locked":false,"text":"SESSION START\n    ↓\n① Load context: root CLAUDE.md + role subdir CLAUDE.md (auto)\n    ↓\n② Open docs/TASKS.md → find next ⬜ task with all deps ✅\n    ↓\n③ 7-STEP LOOP (no exceptions, every task, every role):\n   READ → PLAN → ALIGN → IMPLEMENT → SELF-REVIEW → TEST → DONE\n    ↓\n④ Mark task ✅ in TASKS.md\n    ↓\n⑤ Run /handoff → Claude updates CLAUDE.md §Current Work\n    ↓\nSESSION END\n\n⚠ RULE: /handoff is mandatory. Without it, next session\n   starts from zero. Context is permanently lost.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"SESSION START\n    ↓\n① Load context: root CLAUDE.md + role subdir CLAUDE.md (auto)\n    ↓\n② Open docs/TASKS.md → find next ⬜ task with all deps ✅\n    ↓\n③ 7-STEP LOOP (no exceptions, every task, every role):\n   READ → PLAN → ALIGN → IMPLEMENT → SELF-REVIEW → TEST → DONE\n    ↓\n④ Mark task ✅ in TASKS.md\n    ↓\n⑤ Run /handoff → Claude updates CLAUDE.md §Current Work\n    ↓\nSESSION END\n\n⚠ RULE: /handoff is mandatory. Without it, next session\n   starts from zero. Context is permanently lost.","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":true},

