    {"id":"f3rt","type":"text","x":705,"y":465,"width":652,"height":244,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e2e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":4021,"version":1,"versionNonce":4021,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746748800000,"index":"a40","link":null,"locked":false,"text":"STEP 5 — SELF-REVIEW CHECKLIST (Claude, before marking done)\n\n□ Happy path: core scenario works?\n□ Error path: wrong input, DB fail, service down?\n□ Auth: correct role enforced on every endpoint?\n□ Race condition: any shared state that could conflict?\n□ Security: HMAC verify, amount verify, no injection?\n□ Duplicate: idempotency for non-idempotent operations?\n□ Side effects: all spec-listed effects implemented?\n□ Contract: implementation matches spec field names exactly?\n\nPREFIX SYSTEM (Claude signals to human):\n💡 SUGGESTION — better approach found (optional)\n⚠️ FLAG — conflict or ambiguity (must resolve)\n🚨 RISK — production risk found (stop + decide)\n🔴 STOP — will cause bug if continued\n❓ CLARIFY — need info before proceeding\n🔄 REDIRECT — wrong direction, better path exists","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"STEP 5 — SELF-REVIEW CHECKLIST (Claude, before marking done)\n\n□ Happy path: core scenario works?\n□ Error path: wrong input, DB fail, service down?\n□ Auth: correct role enforced on every endpoint?\n□ Race condition: any shared state that could conflict?\n□ Security: HMAC verify, amount verify, no injection?\n□ Duplicate: idempotency for non-idempotent operations?\n□ Side effects: all spec-listed effects implemented?\n□ Contract: implementation matches spec field names exactly?\n\nPREFIX SYSTEM (Claude signals to human):\n💡 SUGGESTION — better approach found (optional)\n⚠️ FLAG — conflict or ambiguity (must resolve)\n🚨 RISK — production risk found (stop + decide)\n🔴 STOP — will cause bug if continued\n❓ CLARIFY — need info before proceeding\n🔄 REDIRECT — wrong direction, better path exists","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":true},

