    {"id":"f5nt","type":"text","x":40,"y":893,"width":2725,"height":126,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e2e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":6091,"version":1,"versionNonce":6091,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[],"updated":1746748800000,"index":"a74","link":null,"locked":false,"text":"HOW KNOWLEDGE ACCUMULATES ACROSS PROJECTS:\nSession → /handoff updates CLAUDE.md §Current Work  |  Phase end → Lead reconciles spec+API+DB + updates LESSONS_LEARNED.md  |  Project end → LESSONS_LEARNED becomes input for NEXT project bootstrap\n\nDOC STALENESS PREVENTION: Every Tier 2 and Tier 3 doc must have  '> Last verified: YYYY-MM-DD'  at the top. At phase end: open each spec → verify vs API_CONTRACT + DB_SCHEMA. Mismatch → ⚠️ FLAG before next phase.\n\n3 RULES TO REMEMBER:  (1) One Fact, One Home — no copies, only references.  (2) CLAUDE.md is a Map, not Territory — stays < 150 lines, pointers only.  (3) No Spec → No Task → No Code — the 4-level chain is mandatory.\nFull guide: docs/doc_structure/NEW_PROJECT_BOOTSTRAP_GUIDE.md  ·  Bootstrap prompt in guide Appendix A.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"HOW KNOWLEDGE ACCUMULATES ACROSS PROJECTS:\nSession → /handoff updates CLAUDE.md §Current Work  |  Phase end → Lead reconciles spec+API+DB + updates LESSONS_LEARNED.md  |  Project end → LESSONS_LEARNED becomes input for NEXT project bootstrap\n\nDOC STALENESS PREVENTION: Every Tier 2 and Tier 3 doc must have  '> Last verified: YYYY-MM-DD'  at the top. At phase end: open each spec → verify vs API_CONTRACT + DB_SCHEMA. Mismatch → ⚠️ FLAG before next phase.\n\n3 RULES TO REMEMBER:  (1) One Fact, One Home — no copies, only references.  (2) CLAUDE.md is a Map, not Territory — stays < 150 lines, pointers only.  (3) No Spec → No Task → No Code — the 4-level chain is mandatory.\nFull guide: docs/doc_structure/NEW_PROJECT_BOOTSTRAP_GUIDE.md  ·  Bootstrap prompt in guide Appendix A.","lineHeight":1.35,"autoResize":true}
